org.anchoranalysis.test.image

Class MaskFixture

  • Object
    • MaskFixture

  • public class MaskFixture
extends Object
    Creates two or three-dimensional Masks for tests.

    The mask has an area of on pixels that is rectangle (2D) or a cuboid (3D) and otherwise pixels are off.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
